{"tid":2214280,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"城 · 點迷你戶額印鬆綁 425萬沽3年賺兩成","createTime":"2020-09-23T06:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T22:30:12.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"77cf13c6be98f810594dae34bb193a336a0c2e9f","tid":2214280,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T06:44:28.000Z","msg":"主打小型單位的屯門城&middot;點，繼上周錄得首宗二手成交個案後，新近以再有業主趁額外印花稅（SSD）限售期屆滿放售物業套現。美聯分行助理區域經理李進豪表示，上述單位為城 &middot; 點中層G室，實用面積227方呎，屬開放式間隔，外望開揚市景，新近以425萬元成交，實呎18,722元。原業主於2017年9月份以約354.3萬元購入，持貨滿3年，帳面獲利約70.7萬元或約20%。"},{"pid":"be34fe0f16de23c9498b0f36b2dac68610b2741f","tid":2214280,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:14:50.000Z","msg":"賺咁小都走 佛心業主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3801b0fe0ccc1037d622543ebf0f83a453209aa","tid":2214280,"uid":126325,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"咁平放?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓價睇黎跌緊啦"},{"pid":"c3d1e23f594a5f1fdc7947942b8ec2c56574bbe6","tid":2214280,"uid":126325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633603b144dfe718c20b241a583a895d6b44ef26","tid":2214280,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"又話細單位新樓蟹硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68119be81baf399f4831b285ebae695c66c7ef57","tid":2214280,"uid":126325,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"633603b144dfe718c20b241a583a895d6b44ef26","tid":2214280,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor